---
metadata: {
    partial_name: 'Ecommerce | Reviews | Write Review Modal'
}
---
{% comment %}
    Write Review modal (Part A) — shell only.
    The form body is intentionally left blank to be built separately.

    Open from JS with: document.getElementById('review-modal').open()

    Params:
    - reviewed_product : product uuid the review is attached to (available on
                         the body as data-reviewed-product for the form to read)
    - has_profile      : boolean from the parent (check_if_user_has_profile) —
                         selects the logged-in vs guest form variant
{% endcomment %}
<ins-modal id="review-modal" with-backdrop no-button>
    <div class="review-modal-body" data-reviewed-product="{{ reviewed_product }}">
        <h5 class="heading-3">Write a review</h5>
        <div class="spacer"></div>

        {%- include_form 'modules/ins_forms/write_a_review', has_profile, reviewed_product: reviewed_product -%}

    </div>
</ins-modal>
